  "ciliary_role": "Also known as FPC. Functio l and/or structural component of primary cilia in kidney tubular cells (14978161). Mutations are involved in utosomal recessive polycystic kidney disease (15458427, 11898128, 14983006). PKHD1 may associate with a common pathway that alters ciliary function and cation channel activity and may act as an intraflagellar motor-binding protein. It also interacts with polycystins, which suggest it could be directly or indirectly involved in a common cystogenic pathway (14983006).",
